Process called "calculate_average" that takes times as List[Number] returns Number:
    Note: Calculates average of time measurements
    Let total be 0
    For time in times:
        Set total to total plus time
    If length of times is greater than 0:
        Return total divided by (length of times)
    Otherwise:
        Return 0

Process called "get_system_memory_usage" returns Number:
    Note: Gets current system memory usage (simulated)
    Return 1048576

Process called "convert_to_string" that takes value as Any returns String:
